264
00:18:27,628 --> 00:18:30,084
Haru-tan rejected you, right?

265
00:18:31,211 --> 00:18:33,062
I know.

266
00:18:40,580 --> 00:18:42,545
You knew?

267
00:18:43,842 --> 00:18:48,068
But you still love him, don't you?

268
00:18:58,011 --> 00:19:01,429
Why give up after one setback?

269
00:19:01,429 --> 00:19:04,731
How many times did I reject you?

270
00:19:05,925 --> 00:19:11,401
