271
00:19:11,406 --> 00:19:16,789
I fell in love with your unpersuasive passion and clumsy manner.

272
00:19:20,689 --> 00:19:22,312
Choko.

273
00:19:25,215 --> 00:19:31,307
My pride won't allow you to give up on him so easily.

274
00:19:37,844 --> 00:19:42,912
Shall we go together to submit this?

275
